Description: HDAnalyzeR accelerates and simplifies proteomics data analysis for biomarker discovery in disease research. It offers a streamlined suite of tools for tasks including differential expression analysis, classification modeling, dimensionality reduction, imputation, and data visualization. With user-friendly functions and high-quality, publication-ready plots, HDAnalyzeR enables researchers—from clinicians to bioinformaticians—to efficiently explore and interpret omics data, uncovering potential biomarkers in blood plasma with ease and accuracy.
